      • setBaseDiscordUrl

        public static void setBaseDiscordUrl(String url)
        This sets the base discord api so the provided url. This defaults to https://discordapp.com/. NOTE: This will only have any sort of effect if called before the DiscordEndpoints class is initialized, meaning that you MUST call this before any Discord4J calls.
        Parameters:
        url - The url.
